item.title: Who's That Netmon?!?!
item.description: Yes that title was a Pokemon reference, and if you didn't understand it I feel sorry for you. This is my walkthrough of the HTB Netmon box. Enjoy, and find my walkthough below!

item.title: CoCanDa Forever
item.description: It was just a matter of time before a marvel reference came in to play... Follow along with me as we dive into a challenge from Blue Team Labs Online. New website and new fun content as we break apart an email from an alien hostage taker!

item.title: Lame is Cool
item.description: Clever titles for days. This walkthough of the Lame box is another begginner friendly entry level HTB. We'll explore a little anonymous FTP, and find out more about Samba. You can find the walkthrough video down below!

item.title: This is my Legacy
item.description: The clever titles just don't stop! This is my walkthrough of the Legacy HTB. Enjoy, find the video below, and reach out if you have any questions.
